text: Canton of Saint-Malo 2 within Ille-et-Vilaine. The canton of Saint-Malo-2 is an administrative division of the Ille-et-Vilaine department, in northwestern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Saint-Malo.Décret n° 2014-177 du 18 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département d'Ille-et- Vilaine It consists of the following communes: #Dinard #Le Minihic-sur-Rance #Pleurtuit #La Richardais #Saint-Briac-sur-Mer #Saint-Jouan-des-Guérets #Saint-Lunaire #Saint-Malo (partly) ==References== Category:Cantons of Ille- et-Vilaine
